ed="T" n="0781c27"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0781c27"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000017205">福州雪峯廣福院</placeName><persName key="A003677">義存</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0781c28"/><persName key="A003677">釋義存</persName>，<date from-iso="+0822-01-31" key="j20213202021703" to-iso="+0823-02-18"><name>長慶</name>二年壬寅</date>生<anchor xml:id="beg0781007"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0781007"/><placeName key="PL000000017997">泉州南安縣</placeName><name>曾</name><lb
ed="T" n="0781c29"/>氏。自王父<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1306"/>而下，皆友僧親佛，清淨謹愿。<persName key="A003677">存</persName><pb ed="T" n="0782a" xml:id="T50.2061.0782a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0782a01"/>生而鼻逆葷血。乳抱中，或聞鐘磬，或見僧<lb
ed="T" n="0782a02"/>像，其容必動，以是別垂愛於膝下。<date key="j20242432024626" from-iso="+0830-02-01" to-iso="+0831-02-19">九歲</date>請<lb
ed="T" n="0782a03"/>出家，怒而未允。<date key="j20253362025719" from-iso="+0833-01-29" to-iso="+0834-02-16">十二</date>從<ref type="person" target="#A023005">家君</ref>遊<placeName key="PL000000017573">蒲田玉<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>潤</sic><corr>澗</corr></choice><lb
ed="T" n="0782a04"/>寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1639"/>，有律師<persName key="A010602">慶玄</persName><ptr target="#n1640"/>，持行高潔。遽拜之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A003677">我</ref>師<lb
ed="T" n="0782a05"/>也。」遂留為童侍焉。<date key="j20271672027520" from-iso="+0838-02-03" to-iso="+0839-01-22">十七</date>落髮。來謁<placeName key="PL000000057110">芙蓉山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0782a06"/><persName key="A019949">恒照大師</persName><ptr target="#n1641"/>，見而奇之，故止其所<ptr target="#n1642"/>。至<date notBefore-iso="+0846-04-26" key="j20301712035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>宣宗</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0782a07"/>興<name>釋</name>氏，其道也涅而不緇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1603"/>，其身也<anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz4"/>褎<anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz4"/>然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1604"/>而出。<lb
ed="T" n="0782a08"/>北遊<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000010514">楚</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000043857">梁</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025556">宋</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000044976">秦</placeName>，受具足戒於<placeName key="PL000000000358">幽州寶剎<lb
ed="T" n="0782a09"/>寺</placeName>訖<ptr target="#n1643"/>，巡名山，扣諸禪宗，突兀飄颻，雲翔鳥<lb
ed="T" n="0782a10"/>逝。爰及<placeName key="PL000000029413">武陵</placeName>，一面<persName key="A003868">德山</persName><ptr target="#n1644"/>，止於珍重而出<ptr target="#n1645"/>。其<lb
ed="T" n="0782a11"/>徒數百，咸莫測之。<persName key="A003868">德山</persName>曰：「斯無階也，<ref type="person" target="#A003868">吾</ref>得<lb
ed="T" n="0782a12"/>之矣。」<date from-iso="+0865-02-04" key="j20370302037384" to-iso="+0866-01-24"><name>咸通</name>六年</date>，歸于<placeName key="PL000000057110">芙蓉</placeName>之故山。<ref type="date" target="#j20370302037384">其年</ref><persName key="A003636">圓<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>寂</sic><corr>智</corr></choice><lb
ed="T" n="0782a13"/>大師</persName>亦自<placeName key="PL000000028694">溈山</placeName>擁徒至于<placeName key="PL000000057113">怡山</placeName>，<persName key="A023006">王<roleName>真君</roleName></persName>上昇<lb
ed="T" n="0782a14"/>之地<ptr target="#n1646"/>。其徒<ref type="person" target="#A008370">孰</ref>（<ref type="person" target="#A008370"><anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz6"/>就<anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz6"/><roleName>師</roleName></ref>已嗣<persName key="A003868">德山</persName>）<ptr target="#n1647"/>纍纍而<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>疑</sic><corr>款</corr></choice>關<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1605"/>，<persName key="A003677">存</persName>拒而久<lb
ed="T" n="0782a15"/>之。則有<persName key="A023008">行實</persName>者，始以<persName key="A003677">存</persName>同而議曰：「我之道<lb
ed="T" n="0782a16"/>魏魏乎，法門圍遶之所，不可造次<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g619"/>，其地宜<lb
ed="T" n="0782a17"/>若布金<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1606"/>之形勝可矣。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000017165">府</ref>之西二百里有山<lb
ed="T" n="0782a18"/>焉，環控四邑，峭拔萬仞，崷崒以支圓碧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1607"/>，培<lb
ed="T" n="0782a19"/>樓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1608"/>以覛群青。怪石古松，棲蟄龜鶴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1609"/>，靈湫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1610"/>邃壑，<lb
ed="T" n="0782a20"/>隱見龍雷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1611"/>。山之巔，先冬而雪，盛夏而寒。其樹<lb
ed="T" n="0782a21"/>皆別垂藤蘿，<anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz10"/>䒠<anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz10"/>茸而以為之衣，交錯而不<lb
ed="T" n="0782a22"/>呈其形，奇姿異景，不可殫狀。雖<placeName key="PL000000018469">霍童</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000018271">武<lb
ed="T" n="0782a23"/>夷</placeName>，無以加之。實<placeName key="PL000000056178">閩越</placeName>之神秀，而古仙之未<lb
ed="T" n="0782a24"/>攸居，誠有待於我也。祈以偕行<anchor xml:id="beg0782001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>去</sic><corr>（去）</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0782001"/><ptr target="#n253"/>。」<date from-iso="+0870-08-05" key="j20390382039067" to-iso="+0870-09-03">秋七<lb
ed="T" n="0782a25"/>月</date>，穿雲躡蘚，陟險昇幽，將及之，<persName key="A003677">存</persName>曰：「真<lb
ed="T" n="0782a26"/><ref type="person" target="#A003677">吾</ref>居也」<ptr target="#n1660"/>。其夕山之神果効靈，翌日巖谷爽朗，<lb
ed="T" n="0782a27"/>煙霞飛動。雲庵既立，月構旋隆，繇是<ptr type="glossary" target="#g911"/>柅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1612"/>法輪<lb
ed="T" n="0782a28"/>於無為，樹空門於有地。<persName key="A023008">行實</persName>乃請名其山，<lb
ed="T" n="0782a29"/>曰<placeName key="PL000000017136">雪峯</placeName>。以其冬雪夏寒，取<placeName key="PL000000048268">鷲嶺</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000056385">猴江</placeName>之義，<pb ed="T" n="0782b" xml:id="T50.2061.0782b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0782b01"/>斯則<date from-iso="+0870-02-09" key="j20388612039214" to-iso="+0871-01-28">庚寅</date><ptr target="#n1648"/>。逮于<date from-iso="+0875-02-14" key="j20406922041045" to-iso="+0876-02-02">乙未</date>，<persName key="A003677">存</persName>以<ref type="place" target="#PL000000017136">山</ref>而道任，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000017136">山</ref>以<lb
ed="T" n="0782b02"/><persName key="A003677">存</persName>而名出，天下之釋子，不計華夏，趨之若<lb
ed="T" n="0782b03"/>召。<date notBefore-iso="+0874-12-21" key="j20406372042521" notAfter-iso="+0880-02-17"><name>乾符</name>中</date>，觀察使<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName><persName key="A010612">韋<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1649"/>、<date notBefore-iso="+0881-08-13" key="j20430642044395" notAfter-iso="+0885-04-05"><name>中和</name>中</date>司空<placeName key="PL000000024832">穎<lb
ed="T" n="0782b04"/>川</placeName><persName key="A010613">陳<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1650"/>，每渴醍醐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g883"/>而不克就飲，交使馳<lb
ed="T" n="0782b05"/>懇，<persName key="A003677">存</persName>為之入府，從人願也。其時內官有<lb
ed="T" n="0782b06"/>復命于<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，語其道其儕之拔俗悟空者，<lb
ed="T" n="0782b07"/>請蛻浮華而來脫屣<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g356"/>。<persName key="A005228">僖宗皇帝</persName>聞之，翰林<lb
ed="T" n="0782b08"/>學士訪於<placeName key="PL000000017165">閩</placeName>人<persName key="A010607">陳延効</persName>，得其實奏。於是乃<lb
ed="T" n="0782b09"/>錫<persName key="A003677">真覺大師</persName>之號<ptr target="#n402"/>，仍以紫袈裟俾<persName key="A010607">延効</persName><ptr target="#n1651"/>授<lb
ed="T" n="0782b10"/>焉。<persName key="A003677">存</persName>受之如不受，衣之如不衣。居累夏，<lb
ed="T" n="0782b11"/><date from-iso="+0891-02-17" key="j20465392046567" to-iso="+0891-03-17">辛亥歲朔</date>，遽然杖屨。其徒啟而不答，雲以隨<lb
ed="T" n="0782b12"/>之，東浮于<placeName key="PL000000014380">丹丘</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>。<date from-iso="+0892-02-06" key="j20468932047247" to-iso="+0893-01-25">明年</date>，屬<persName key="A003732">王<roleName>侍中</roleName></persName>之始<lb
ed="T" n="0782b13"/>據<placeName key="PL000000056178">閩越</placeName>，乃洗兵於法雨，致禮於禪林，馥<persName key="A003677">存</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0782b14"/>之道，常東望頂手。<date from-iso="+0894-02-14" key="j20476322047985" to-iso="+0895-02-02">後二年</date>自<placeName key="PL000000008355">吳</placeName>還<placeName key="PL000000017165">閩</placeName>，大加<lb
ed="T" n="0782b15"/>禮異。及<persName key="A003732">閩王王<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>誓眾養民之外，雅隆其<lb
ed="T" n="0782b16"/>道，凡齋僧構剎，必請問焉。為之增宇、設像、<lb
ed="T" n="0782b17"/>鑄鐘以嚴其山，優施以充其眾。時則迎而<lb
ed="T" n="0782b18"/>館之于府之東西甲第。每將儼油幢、聆法<lb
ed="T" n="0782b19"/>論，未嘗不移時。僅乎一紀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g122"/>，勤勤懇懇，熊羆<lb
ed="T" n="0782b20"/>之士<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1613"/>，因之投跡檀那；漁獵之逸，其或弭心鱗<lb
ed="T" n="0782b21"/>羽。<date from-iso="+0908-04-09" key="j20527992052827" to-iso="+0908-05-07">戊辰年春三月</date>示疾，<persName key="A003732">閩王</persName>走醫，醫至粒<lb
ed="T" n="0782b22"/>藥以授，<persName key="A003677">存</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A003677">吾</ref>非疾也，不可罔子之工。」卒<lb
ed="T" n="0782b23"/>不餌之。其後札偈以遺法子，函翰以別王<lb
ed="T" n="0782b24"/>庭。<date key="j20528592052859" when-iso="+0908-06-08">夏五月二日</date>，鳥獸悲鳴，雲木慘悴<ptr target="#n1652"/>。其夜十<lb
ed="T" n="0782b25"/>有八刻<ptr target="#n1653"/>時滅度，俗壽八十有七，僧臘五十有<lb
ed="T" n="0782b26"/>九。以<date key="j20528722052872" when-iso="+0908-06-21">其月十五日</date>塔而藏之<ptr target="#n1661"/>。爾日奔走，<placeName key="PL000000017165">閩</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0782b27"/>之僧尼士庶，巷無居人。<persName key="A003732">閩王</persName>漣如出涕，且<lb
ed="T" n="0782b28"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A003677">師</ref>其捨予，一何遽乎！」遣子<persName key="A010609">延稟</persName><ptr target="#n1654"/>躬祭奠<lb
ed="T" n="0782b29"/>之，復齋僧焉。<persName key="A003677">存</persName>之行化四十餘年，四方之僧<pb ed="T" n="0782c" xml:id="T50.2061.0782c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0782c01"/>爭趨法席者不可勝算矣，冬夏不減一千<lb
ed="T" n="0782c02"/>五百徒之環足其趨也。馳而愈離，辯而愈<lb
ed="T" n="0782c03"/>惑<ptr target="#n1655"/>。其庶幾者，一曰<persName key="A008370">師備</persName>，擁徒于<placeName key="PL000000057277">玄沙</placeName><ptr target="#n1656"/>（今<placeName key="PL000000017144">安國</placeName>也<ptr target="#n1709"/>）；次<lb
ed="T" n="0782c04"/>曰<persName key="A010610">可休</persName>，擁徒于<placeName key="PL000000013162">越州洞巖</placeName>；次曰<persName key="A010611">智孚</persName>，擁徒<lb
ed="T" n="0782c05"/>于<placeName key="PL000000020127">信州鵝湖</placeName>；其四曰<persName key="A003890">惠稜</persName>，擁徒于<placeName key="PL000000017888">泉州招<lb
ed="T" n="0782c06"/>慶</placeName>；其五曰<persName key="A003900">神晏</persName>，住<placeName key="PL000000017165">福州</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000017193">鼓山</placeName>。分燈化物，<lb
ed="T" n="0782c07"/>皆膺聖獎，賜紫袈裟，而<persName key="A008370">玄沙</persName>級<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1615"/><persName key="A008370">宗一大師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0782c08"/>焉。</p><p><lb
ed="T" n="0782c09"/>系曰：<persName key="A003677">雪峯</persName>道也恢廓乎！駿奔四海學人。所出<lb
ed="T" n="0782c10"/>門生形色不類，何邪？<persName key="A008370">玄沙</persName>乘《楞嚴》<ptr target="#n92"/>而入道，<lb
ed="T" n="0782c11"/>識見天殊，其猶諺曰「青成藍，藍謝青，師何<lb
ed="T" n="0782c12"/><anchor xml:id="beg0782002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>甞</sic><corr>常</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0782002"/>，在明經。」<ptr target="#n1657"/>故有過師之說。一則<persName key="A003677">雪峯</persName>自述，<lb
ed="T" n="0782c13"/>塔銘已盡其致也<ptr target="#n1658"/>。一則<persName key="A008370">玄沙</persName>安立三句<ptr target="#n1659"/>，決<lb
ed="T" n="0782c14"/>擇群見，極成洞過歟！今<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>多尚斯學，此<lb
ed="T" n="0782c15"/>學虛通，無繫了達，逍遙勿拘，知「乘急」也。<persName key="A003677">雪<lb
ed="T" n="0782c16"/>峯</persName>化眾，切乎杜默禪坐，知「戒急」也。其能各<lb
ed="T" n="0782c17"/>捨一緩，以成一全，則可乎！</p>
